# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Project-specific (per request)
# NOTE: git does NOT support trailing inline comments on patterns,
# so every comment lives on its own line.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Course material / group deliverables — kept private
assignments/

# Claude's working notes & scratchpad
claude/

# datasets/: the small public UCI zips ARE tracked (teammate convenience — see negations
# in the Data section below). The multi-GB files (food.parquet, pmdata.zip) stay ignored —
# GitHub rejects files >100MB; share those out of band (drive link / Git LFS).

# NOTE: docs/ is intentionally TRACKED (version-controlled) — decided 2026-06-13.

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Secrets & environment  (NEVER commit — security-first project)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.env
secrets/
*.key
*.pem
*.crt
*.p12
*.pfx
credentials.json
service-account*.json

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Python
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.so
.Python
build/
develop-eggs/
dist/
downloads/
eggs/
.eggs/
/lib/
/lib64/
parts/
sdist/
var/
wheels/
*.egg-info/
.installed.cfg
*.egg
.venv/
venv/
env/
ENV/
.python-version
.pytest_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.coverage
htmlcov/
.tox/
.hypothesis/

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Node / frontend (if/when added)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
node_modules/
.next/
out/
.nuxt/
dist-ssr/
*.local
.pnpm-store/
.parcel-cache/
.cache/
coverage/
.vite/

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Data — never commit real or generated personal data
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
data/
*.csv
*.tsv
*.parquet
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3
*.db
*.zip
# …but DO track the small public UCI datasets (teammate convenience, ~56KB total).
!datasets/student+performance.zip
!datasets/student+academics+performance.zip
dumps/
backups/
# keep tracked reference schema SQL
!**/schema/*.sql

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Docker / runtime volumes
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.pid
*.log
logs/
pgdata/
mongodata/
volumes/

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
